title: Above & Beyond 55+ Living In a 2 BR Apt at The Legends of Woodbury!
map_address: 570 Settlers Ridge Parkway near Hudson Rd
posting_body: ['The Legends of Woodbury brings brand new independent 55+ living to your neighborhood!', 'Our community offers spacious one, two and three bedroom apartment homes.', 'Conveniently located near parks,shopping, and restaurants.', 'Our community offers the freedoms of contemporary maintenance-free living combined with amenities such as a full size washer/dryer in every home and underground heated parking.', 'The Legends of Woodbury also features beautifully appointed community spaces, including a community room, fitness center, craft/card room, and landscaped outdoor patio.', 'NOTE: Office Hours - By Appointment Only.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- 2-Story Clubhouse', '- Close to Grocery Stores, Restaurants, Coffee Shops & More!', '- Open & Spacious Floor Plans', '- Outdoor Dog Run', '- Theater Room', '- Private Patio or Balcony Space (select homes)', '- Professional On-Site Management Team', '- Full-Size Washer & Dryer', 'In EVERY Home!', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Legends of Woodbury is a community for active seniors that participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'At least one household member must be at least 55 years of age.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Legends of Woodbury', '570 Settlers Ridge Parkway', 'Woodbury, MN, 55129', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'fMbt6oXkafhM']
